# v3.31 A: project-specific guard patterns extension (loaded by
# .github/workflows/guard-strategic-files.yml when present). Keeping
# the specifics here instead of inlined in the workflow yaml stops
# the path patterns from being broadcast in the public CI config.
.guardignore

# v3.31: project-specific internal-disclosure regexes loaded by
# scripts/release_sanitize_check.py --internal. Kept out of the public
# script so it doesn't broadcast which specifics we scrub.
.sanitizeignore

# v3.31 P1-3: internal docs (CHANGELOG-internal.md and any other
# maintainer-only notes that hold review codes / debugging detail /
# strategy). The public CHANGELOG.md ships; this dir never does.
docs/internal/

