docs/messaging.md
docs/vision.md

# Internal R&D / evaluation methodology — the ENTIRE experiments/ tree
# is maintainer-only (eval judge model selection, scoring rubrics,
# per-round reports, audit harnesses, router/coordinator prototypes).
# Strategic signal, not user-facing reproducibility. Kept local; never
# published. (The specific sub-patterns below are now subsumed by this
# blanket rule but kept for documentation of intent.)
experiments/

